prompts.frontCover: A humorous and enchanting birthday scene featuring cartoon-style illustrations of Lao Lao and Jordan. Lao Lao is depicted as a pampered queen, lounging regally on an ornate, oversized throne made of twisting, luminous moonstone and adorned with flowering vines. She wears an elegant, flowing gown in a shade of soft blue and a delicate, sparkling crown, looking very pleased with herself. Beside the throne, Jordan is portrayed as a devoted and slightly comical royal guard. He is kneeling, wearing a humorously formal guard's uniform, and attentively feeding a single, plump grape to Lao Lao. In his other hand, he holds a gigantic, lush tropical leaf, fanning her with an earnest expression. The entire scene is set in a magical, dreamy garden at twilight, with oversized, glowing flora, sparkling fireflies, and soft, ethereal light filtering through a fantasy forest background. The overall art style is flat 2D illustration with a whimsical, storybook quality and a palette of pastel and jewel tones. In the center, the words "Happy Birthday, Queen Lao Lao" are written in a beautiful, flowing handwritten cursive script.
